{"tid":721924,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（中愛神箭）晚晚十二個鐘不停錫","createTime":"2018-06-29T05:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T11:24:51.000Z","uid":80527,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6915937052d9c9034738298564fb244b524b78","tid":721924,"uid":80527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"無誇張，我知講出口好唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但已經幾晚都係咁，一對望就錫<br />\n廁所都忍一陣先去，無野做，就只係抱同錫<br />\n錫到嘴都爛，一望到好自然甜笑，當然都有傾計<br />\n我覺得我地真係好似愛情電影入面嘅主角<br />\n每次走都好唔捨得，拖好耐先走到<br />\n明明已經幾乎日日見，點解會咁？<br />\n係愛定激情定迷戀⋯⋯<br />\n以前拍拖熱戀期間都無咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雙方都解釋唔到點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好幸福，但怕承載唔到<br />\n有無巴絲試過呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481aba3b7ae24fca7c12e09622a2094289acae81","tid":721924,"uid":138138,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"〃&times;\\★＿原來〃當愛變成習慣後‥．只會更深&prime;更逼"},{"pid":"68c658c2b74083235232a7684b992e5279b494cb","tid":721924,"uid":80527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481aba3b7ae24fca7c12e09622a2094289acae81","tid":721924,"uid":138138,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"〃&times;\\★＿原來〃當愛變成習慣後‥．只會更深&prime;更逼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcf1209bdc5af36af96c17df2682e1da56c7b3b","tid":721924,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68c658c2b74083235232a7684b992e5279b494cb","tid":721924,"uid":80527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481aba3b7ae24fca7c12e09622a2094289acae81","tid":721924,"uid":138138,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"〃&t